      "cooked": "<p>Sic do citonte Alba me zamete dhe e ftohur ngambrapa, po me ate ngapara ende ne rregull</p>\n<p>Let all bitterness and wrath and anger and clamor and slander be put away from you, along with all malice. [Ephesians 4:31-32]</p>\n<p>What causes quarrels and what causes fights among you? Is it not this, that your passions are at war within you? [[James 4:1]</p>\n<p>Ndersa une do citoja Hygone, po ne gjuhen barbare qe e kupton  Alba me zamete dhe e ftohur ngambrapa, qe te mos perdore Google-in si i Mothi nga frengjishtja</p>\n<p>The wicked envy and hate; it is their way of admiring.</p>",
      "reply_to_post_number": null,
      "like_count": 0
