      "avatar_template": "/user_avatar/peshkupauje.com/pjetermustakuqi/{size}/11417_2.png",
      "created_at": "2019-09-12T20:52:50.458Z",
      "cooked": "<aside class=\"quote no-group\" data-username=\"xhatani\" data-post=\"16\" data-topic=\"5201\">\n<div class=\"title\">\n<div class=\"quote-controls\"></div>\n<img loading=\"lazy\" alt=\"\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" src=\"https://peshkupauje.com/letter_avatar_proxy/v4/letter/x/13edae/48.png\" class=\"avatar\"> xhatani:</div>\n<blockquote>\n<p>r. Fundja te gjithe ata qe vune interesat kombetare mbi ato personale , per mua konsiderohet shqiptar te medhenj.</p>\n</blockquote>\n</aside>\n<p>Manush Myftiu ka vene pasurine e tij ne sherbim te luftes, Haxhi Lleshi gjithashtu - a quhen shqiptare te medhenj keta?<br>\nPs<br>\nPer mu po.</p>",
      "reply_to_post_number": 16,
      "like_count": 0
    },
    {
